import { Field, Formik } from 'formik'
import './login.css'
export default function Login() {
    return (
        <Formik>
            <Form>
                <Field
                    type="email"
                    name="email"
                    placeholder="Enter your Email"
                    title="Enter your email"
                    required={true}


                >



                </Field>



            </Form>
        </Formik>
    )

}
